Internal wrapper function to calculate MSY reference points (now using MSYCalcs)

Source: R/popdyn.R
optMSY_eq.Rd

Internal wrapper function to calculate MSY reference points (now using MSYCalcs)

optMSY_eq(
  x,
  M_ageArray,
  Wt_age,
  Mat_age,
  Fec_age,
  V,
  maxage,
  R0,
  SRrel,
  hs,
  SSBpR,
  yr.ind = 1,
  plusgroup = 0
)

Arguments

x

Simulation number

M_ageArray

Array of M-at-age

Wt_age

Array of weight-at-age

Mat_age

Array of maturity-at-age

Fec_age

Array of relative fecundity-at-age (spawning biomass weight)

V

Array of selectivity-at-age

maxage

Vector of maximum age

R0

Vector of R0s

SRrel

SRR type

hs

Vector of steepness

SSBpR

Vector of unfished spawners per recruit

yr.ind

Year index used in calculations

plusgroup

Integer. Default = 0 = no plus-group. Use 1 to include a plus-group

Value

Results from MSYCalcs
